# Design System Contribution

## When to Add a Token

- Add a new token when a value repeats across components.
- Use inline styles only for one-off experiments.

## Component Rules

- Forward refs when wrapping RN primitives.
- Accept DS props first (`variant`, `size`, etc.).
- Hoist `style` last in the prop order.

```tsx
export const Button = forwardRef<View, ButtonProps>(
  ({ variant = 'primary', style, ...rest }, ref) => (
    <Pressable ref={ref} style={[variantStyles[variant], style]} {...rest} />
  )
)
```

## Theming

